.TH MNEMOSYNE-INGEST-UPDATE 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne ingest-update \- Incrementally update the knowledge graph from changed files.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne ingest-update\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Incrementally update the knowledge graph from changed files.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fBpath\fR
Directory to scan (default: ~/mnemosyne/raw/)
.TP
\fB\-\-domain\fR
Domain filter (default: auto)
.TP
\fB\-\-scope\-id\fR
Attach a scope ID to updated entities
.TP
\fB\-\-prune\fR
Remove cache entries for files that no longer exist
.TP
\fB\-\-stats\fR
Show stats only, do not re\-extract
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be updated without writing to the knowledge graph
.TP
\fB\-\-wiki\-root\fR
LLM Wiki root (default: ~/mnemosyne/wiki)
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-wiki\fR
Do not update Markdown LLM Wiki pages
.TP
\fB\-\-wiki\-excerpts\fR
Opt in to bounded, redacted source excerpts in wiki source pages
.TP
\fB\-\-examples\fR
Show update examples and output format details
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
